    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2013-05-24</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2013-07-03T19:14:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Border Communities Economic Security and Sustainability Act of 2013 - Directs the Secretary of Homeland Security (DHS) and the Administrator of the General Services Administration (GSA) to coordinate to ensure that appropriate measures are taken to accommodate preexisting and border location-dependent businesses into the design and construction of reconfigured and new ports of entry.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Border Communities Economic Security and Sustainability Act of 2013</title>
